The underlying technology was featured on the cover of Science Translational Medicine in 2023. Optimized, precision treatment strategies developed by our AI platform have the potential to significantly improve quality of care, boost efficiency, and reduce cost of perinatal care. Our first product is focused on **AI-driven nutrition** for premature newborns. A successful pilot on ordering of appropriate total parenteral nutrition (TPN) prescriptions has already been performed at Stanford Children's Health (n=180).
